    "introduction": "他在23岁时被称为中国最年轻的独立导演。当其他80后艺术家在狂热的追逐潮流，林哲乐导演依然坚持忠于他自己独特的叙事手法：感性又理智，渊博又朴素。他锐利的视觉语言和律动节奏，打开了他进入当代中国艺术和电影市场的大门。He was titled China’s youngest indie-director at 23. While most of so-called post 80s artists grow infatuated with trend hunting, Zero stays loyal and patient developing his unique style: emotional yet unsentimental, profound yet unadorned. His keen visual language and rhythmic charisma opened his door to the world to China’s contemporary art museums and innovative film proposals.",
